![](u2-d14-effective-dataviz_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-14-1.png){fig-align='center' width=60%}
:::
:::
]

.panel[.panel-name[Code]

`fct_rev`: Reverse order of factor levels

::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(brexit, aes(y = fct_rev(region))) + #<<
  geom_bar()
```
:::
]

]

---


## Clean up labels

.panelset[

.panel[.panel-name[Plot]

::: {.cell layout-align="center"}
::: {.cell-output-display}
![](u2-d14-effective-dataviz_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-15-1.png){fig-align='center' width=60%}
:::
:::

]

.panel[.panel-name[Code]


::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(brexit, aes(y = fct_rev(region))) +
  geom_bar() +
  labs( #<<
    x = "Count", #<<
    y = "Region" #<<
  ) #<<
```
:::

]

]


